query:
-- Check current counts
SELECT 
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM counties) as total_agencies,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM protocolChunks) as total_protocols,
  (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT state) FROM counties) as total_states;
